<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>为什么需要一级缓存？</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><strong><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一级缓存也叫本地缓存</span></strong></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis </span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的一级缓存是在会话（</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）层面进行缓存的</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的一级缓存是默认开启的，不需要任何的配置。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">执行的流程里面，涉及到这么多的对象，那么缓存</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">PerpetualCache </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">应该放在哪个对象里面去维护？如果要在</span><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">同一个会话</span></strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">里面</span><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">共享</span></strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一级缓存，这个对象肯定是在</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">里面创建的，作为</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的一个属性。</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span></span><span
        style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span></span><br></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DefaultSqlSession </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">里面只有两个属性，</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Configuration </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是全局的，所以缓存只可能放在</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Executor </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">里面维护</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">每当我们使用</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">开启一次和数据库的会话，</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">会创建出一个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象表示一次数据库会话。</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffcc"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在同一个会话里面，多次执行相同的</span></span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffcc"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SQL </span></span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffcc"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">语句，会直接从内存取到缓存的结果，不会再发送</span></span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffcc"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SQL </span></span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffcc"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">到数据库</span></span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffff"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">不同的会话里面，即使执行的</span></span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffff"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SQL </span></span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffff"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一模一样（通过一个</span></span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffff"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Mapper </span></span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#ccffff"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的同一个方法的相同参数调用），也不能使用到一级缓存</span></span></span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在对数据库的一次会话中，我们有可能会反复地执行完全相同的查询语句，如果不采取一些措施的话，</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">每一次查询都会查询一次数据库</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">,</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:#dbe5f1"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">而我们在极短的时间内做了完全相同的查询，这有可能造成很大的资源浪费</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，因为它们的结果极有可能完全相同。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>一级缓存（本地缓存）</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">为了解决这一问题，</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">会在一次会话中，一个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象中创建一个本地缓存</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">(local
                cache)</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，对于每一次查询，都会尝试根据查询的条件去本地缓存中查找是否在缓存中，如果在缓存中，就直接从缓存中取出，然后返回给用户；否则，从数据库读取数据，将查询结果存入缓存并返回给用户</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><img
        src="data:image/png;base64,"
        style="height:179px; width:401px"></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>一级缓存的不足</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">使用一级缓存的时候，因为缓存不能跨会话共享，不同的会话之间对于相同的数据可能有不一样的缓存。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">在有多个会话或者分布式环境下，会存在脏数据的问题。如果要解决这个问题，就要用到二级缓存。</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一级缓存（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBaits </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">称其为</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Local Cache</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）无法关闭，但是有两种级别可选：</span></span>
        <ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
            <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">session
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">级别的缓存，在同一个</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> sqlSession
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">内，对同样的查询将不再查询数据库，直接从缓存中</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">statement
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">级别的缓存（将一级缓存的级别设为</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> statement
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">级别的，这样每次查询结束都会清掉一级缓存）</span></span></li>
        </ol>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
